{"tid":2266812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上網買返黎既野比屋企人當垃圾掉左","createTime":"2020-11-01T15:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T15:32:54.000Z","uid":25129,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cefcc40a60a23b475e7877021a3697688a90f34d","tid":2266812,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"岩岩收工返到屋企<br />\n我就問老母「阿媽，我有袋衫擺左係度架喎，你係咪拎左去洗？」<br />\n之後佢同老豆竟然答我當左係垃圾掉左。<br />\n<br />\n我第一時間真係笑左出聲，一路笑一路問佢地係咪戅鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（可能當下已經嬲到SHOT撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n佢地知道瀨野<br />\n之後係咁道歉，又叫我唔好嬲，話比返錢我買返。<br />\n但我都冇理到佢地.....心諗錢唔係問題<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況咁大個仔第一次遇到.....錢好小事，問題佢地真係實在太戅鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f357f40fc77c74771995ca7a3d10f5f4fd1a544","tid":2266812,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:11:43.000Z","msg":"證明你買埋啲垃圾又亂咁擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef21ed52c18e0971a85d4148688bb7d18f99be2","tid":2266812,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"咩牌子咩包裝先？<br />\n順豐包裝就你老豆做得正確啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514289bd812eadb799d05e1294bed5a4878813ab","tid":2266812,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:18:07.000Z","msg":"你話係fashion brand紙袋又禮盒咁<br />\n都掉嘅話就佢地戇鳩啫"},{"pid":"541dc1652b269a9dbfc7828f00924090ad2f30dd","tid":2266812,"uid":25129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef21ed52c18e0971a85d4148688bb7d18f99be2","tid":2266812,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"咩牌子咩包裝先？<br />\n順豐包裝就你老豆做得正確啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20